Require agentgrep

Output docs/_static/demos/vhs/agentgrep-search-field.gif
Output docs/_static/demos/vhs/agentgrep-search-field.mp4
Output docs/_static/demos/vhs/agentgrep-search-field.webm

Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 300
Source docs/_static/demos/vhs/_preamble.tape

Sleep 1s
Type "agentgrep search 'agent:codex timeout'"
Enter
Wait
Sleep 3s
